After rearranging the differential equation in Eq. (1) and taking integral from both sides, the function g(a) in Table A1 can be created:
2∫0adafa=∫0tkdt⇒ga=kt\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
